      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WICKEDLY SMOOTH (4) is colt by McWicked making his debut for Amanda Turnbull. Won his latest trial here and draws to push forward. Could kick off with a win. HESINHEAVENNOW (3) is a colt by Huntsville on debut for Olivia Frisby. Showed improvement in winning his latest trial and is likely to get the favours from this nice draw. IM THE MAJOR (5) is a son of leading sire Art Major stepping out for the first time. One of four acceptors for Bernie Hewitt in this race and he looks to have some ability based on a recent trial win here. Anticipating a bright start to his career. King Of Swing gelding KINGS LEGACY (1) is another from the Bernie Hewitt camp. Has placed in both of his trials and the ace draw is an aid to an inexperienced juvenile.",
